@startuml
title Koa.js Web Application - Request Flow and Connectivity

actor Client
participant "Nginx\n(Reverse Proxy)" as Nginx
participant "PM2\n(Process Manager)" as PM2
participant "Koa Application\n(app.js)" as KoaApp
participant "Middleware Chain" as Middleware
participant "Router" as Router
participant "Controller" as Controller
participant "DAO\n(Data Access)" as DAO
participant "Mongoose\n(ODM)" as Mongoose
database "MongoDB" as MongoDB
participant "Session Store\n(koa-generic-session)" as Session

== HTTP Request Processing ==

Client -> Nginx: HTTP Request
activate Nginx
Nginx -> PM2: Forward Request
activate PM2
PM2 -> KoaApp: Route to App Instance
activate KoaApp

KoaApp -> Middleware: ctx (context)
activate Middleware

Middleware -> Middleware: koa-compose\n(v1 middleware)
Middleware -> Middleware: koa-convert\n(v2 middleware)
Middleware -> Session: Load Session
activate Session
Session -> MongoDB: Retrieve Session Data
activate MongoDB
MongoDB --> Session: Session Data
deactivate MongoDB
Session --> Middleware: Session Context
deactivate Session

Middleware -> Router: Next Middleware
activate Router
Router -> Router: Match Route
Router -> Controller: Invoke Handler
activate Controller

== Business Logic & Data Access ==

Controller -> DAO: Query/Command
activate DAO
DAO -> Mongoose: Model Operation\n(CRUD)
activate Mongoose
Mongoose -> MongoDB: Execute Query
MongoDB --> Mongoose: Result Set
deactivate MongoDB
Mongoose --> DAO: Processed Data
deactivate Mongoose
DAO --> Controller: Domain Objects
deactivate DAO

Controller -> Controller: Process Business Logic
Controller --> Router: Response Data
deactivate Controller
Router --> Middleware: Response Context
deactivate Router

== Session & Response ==

Middleware -> Session: Update Session
activate Session
Session -> MongoDB: Persist Session
activate MongoDB
MongoDB --> Session: Confirmation
deactivate MongoDB
Session --> Middleware: Complete
deactivate Session

Middleware --> KoaApp: Final Context
deactivate Middleware
KoaApp --> PM2: HTTP Response
deactivate KoaApp
PM2 --> Nginx: Response
deactivate PM2
Nginx --> Client: HTTP Response
deactivate Nginx

== AJAX Request Flow ==

Client -> KoaApp: AJAX/XMLHttpRequest
activate Client
activate KoaApp
KoaApp -> Middleware: Process Request
activate Middleware
Middleware -> Router: API Route
activate Router
Router -> Controller: RESTful Handler
activate Controller
Controller -> DAO: Data Operation
activate DAO
DAO -> Mongoose: Query
activate Mongoose
Mongoose -> MongoDB: Fetch Data
activate MongoDB
MongoDB --> Mongoose: JSON Data
deactivate MongoDB
Mongoose --> DAO: Models
deactivate Mongoose
DAO --> Controller: Result
deactivate DAO
Controller --> Router: JSON Response
deactivate Controller
Router --> Middleware: API Response
deactivate Router
Middleware --> KoaApp: Response
deactivate Middleware
KoaApp --> Client: JSON/AJAX Response
deactivate KoaApp
deactivate Client

== Form Submission Flow ==

Client -> Nginx: POST Form Data
activate Nginx
activate Client
Nginx -> PM2: Forward POST
activate PM2
PM2 -> KoaApp: Handle Form
activate KoaApp
KoaApp -> Middleware: Parse Body
activate Middleware
Middleware -> Middleware: Content-Type Handler
Middleware -> Router: Route POST
activate Router
Router -> Controller: Form Handler
activate Controller
Controller -> DAO: Create/Update
activate DAO
DAO -> Mongoose: Save Model
activate Mongoose
Mongoose -> Mongoose: Schema Validation
Mongoose -> Mongoose: Pre-save Hooks
Mongoose -> MongoDB: Insert/Update
activate MongoDB
MongoDB --> Mongoose: Write Result
deactivate MongoDB
Mongoose -> Mongoose: Post-save Hooks
Mongoose --> DAO: Saved Model
deactivate Mongoose
DAO --> Controller: Success
deactivate DAO
Controller --> Router: Redirect/Response
deactivate Controller
Router --> Middleware: Response
deactivate Router
Middleware --> KoaApp: Final Response
deactivate Middleware
KoaApp --> PM2: Response
deactivate KoaApp
PM2 --> Nginx: Response
deactivate PM2
Nginx --> Client: Redirect/Confirmation
deactivate Nginx
deactivate Client

@enduml
